description: Spacious, Junior One-Bedroom on a high floor with a very pretty city view. Apartment needs updating and is sold as is. An opportunity for someone to develop into a good investment. The building has undergone extensive renovations. It boasts a brand new-lobby, world-class health spa and located in the best neighborhood, the New East Side of Chicago
